data.description:
What a fabulous find in Hampstead! This is one of those outstanding homes that impresses you more and more at every turn. From upgraded interiors to a stunning view to a hidden gem in the basement - you really must see this one in person to understand how unique it is!  From the street it's hard to believe all this house has to offer. But walk up to the cozy front porch and step inside, you're going to love it here! The current homeowners have taken excellent care of the property and have made lots of upgrades. Removing the columns from the dining area really opened things up. And new flooring in the full bathroom on this level is lovely. But wait until you see the kitchen! Just fabulous! It has been beautifully remodeled and has loads of storage. Off the foyer, the bedroom is currently being used as an office and comes complete with a Murphy bed. The desk is negotiable if you'd like to keep this perfect room as-is.Upstairs you'll find the very large primary suite with impressive closet space and gracious ensuite. This retreat is the perfect place to unwind and rejuvenate. The old loft was converted to a bedroom giving you three additional bedrooms on this level. You'll also find the laundry room on this level which is so convenient!Now head down to the basement to check out the real star of the show. Everything you could ever want is right here in your own home! Gym space - you've got the perfect set up. Bar area - the wall shelving and custom bar (negotiable) are the ideal spot to entertain. Additional office space - check out the built in desks. Family room - yes, that's here, too. But the coolest spot in the house is hidden behind the mirror. A gentle push opens this secret door to unveil the movie room of your dreams. The theater seating, beanbags and projector stay with the house. No need to unpack the first night! Curl up with friends, family, neighbors, or binge a show all on your own. This place is awesome! Don't forget to check out the backyard and your beautiful view! The lot is over an acre so you have limitless options back here. Dogs, kids, gardening, entertaining - everyone is going to love this yard!

And if all that isn't enough, the location is second to nne. Dogwood Lakes is tucked just off Hwy 17 right between Hampstead and Jacksonville. Not only is this the ideal location for a commute in either direction, this is also the perfect spot to access the beach! Even though your mailing address is Hampstead, you are covered by all the amenities offered by Surf City - including beach parking! Like to travel? You have several airports nearby. 

Give me a call and let's see this one TODAY!
